---
import BaseLayout from "../components/BaseLayout.astro";
import Hero from "../components/Hero.astro";
---
<BaseLayout>
  <Hero
    home
    kicker="Full-stack Builder · AICoding · Independent Apps"
    title="MrFung"
    zh="全栈开发者，AICoding 实践者，独立产品打磨者。把工程能力、产品直觉和耐力运动里的长期主义放在一起，做真实能用、能持续维护的工具。"
    en="Full-stack builder, AICoding practitioner, and independent product maker. I combine engineering, product taste, and endurance-sport discipline to build useful tools that can be maintained for the long run."
  >
    <div class="hero-tag-grid" aria-label="Profile highlights">
      <span>ITRA 430</span>
      <span>马拉松大众二级 / Marathon Amateur Level 2</span>
      <span>有为青年 / Purpose-driven builder</span>
      <span>红十字救护员 / Red Cross first aider</span>
      <span>越野跑 / Trail running</span>
      <span>划桨板 / Paddleboarding</span>
    </div>
    <div class="mf-actions">
      <a class="button primary" href="/apps/">应用 / Apps</a>
      <a class="button" href="/writing/">文章 / Writing</a>
      <a class="button" href="/about/">关于 / About</a>
    </div>
  </Hero>

  <main>
    <section class="section">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <h2>入口 / Directory & Writing</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-grid">
        <article class="feature">
          <div>
            <small>Directory</small>
            <h3>应用目录 / App Directory</h3>
            <p>BillLoopr、RosterSlate、隐私政策和支持入口。</p>
            <p>BillLoopr, RosterSlate, privacy policies, and support links.</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/apps/">查看 / View</a>
        </article>
        <article class="feature">
          <div>
            <small>Writing</small>
            <h3>文章 / Writing</h3>
            <p>全栈、AICoding、独立产品和运动实践。</p>
            <p>Full-stack, AICoding, product craft, and endurance practice.</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/writing/">阅读 / Read</a>
        </article>
        <article class="feature">
          <div>
            <small>Public Pages</small>
            <h3>隐私与支持 / Privacy & Support</h3>
            <p>产品说明、隐私政策、支持方式和联系入口。</p>
            <p>Product notes, privacy policies, support options, and contact links.</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/apps/">全部入口 / All Links</a>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <h2>文章 / Writing</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="writing-list">
        <article class="article-card">
          <div>
            <span class="lang-label">Interior Design</span>
            <h3>怪兽小太阳驿站设计</h3>
            <p>越野品牌办公、会客、展陈、赞助商接待与沿街立面的完整空间方案。</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/writing/monster-sun-station-design/">阅读 / Read</a>
        </article>
        <article class="article-card">
          <div>
            <span class="lang-label">Profile</span>
            <h3>自我介绍：把工程、AICoding 和耐力运动放在一起</h3>
            <p>关于全栈、AICoding、独立产品和耐力运动的简短介绍。</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/writing/self-introduction/">阅读 / Read</a>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</BaseLayout>
